## 📂 Files to Include in Your Repository

Make sure these files are in your `BankShieldAI` folder before pushing:

- `index.html`
- `api.py`
- `requirements.txt`
- `README.md` (copy from above)
- `fraud_model.json` (your trained model)
- `feature_names.json` (feature order)

### Optional but good for deployment:
- `Procfile` (for Render)
- `.gitignore` (to ignore `__pycache__` and `.pkl` backups)

